high_descs: Walk forward and then turn right to approach the sink in the kitchen
Pick up the green apple from the sink
Turn around and walk up to the microwave above the stove
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it, then remove it
Turn left and walk over to the fridge
Put the apple in the fridge to the left of the bread loaf
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked green apple in the fridge

high_descs: Walk forward and around the kitchen island to get to the sink.
Pick up the green apple in the sink.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Walk left to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the apple on the middle shelf in the middle of the other two food items.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink
Pick up the green apple that is on the right side of the sink.
With the apple in hand turn and go to the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside on the right side.  Shut the door and start the microwave.  Open the door and grab the apple.
With the apple in hand go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door while holding the apple in the other hand.  Place the apple on the top shelf in front of and between the tomato and bread.  Shut the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Warm up apple to put in fridge.

high_descs: Move forward and then turn right to find the sink in the island.
Pick up the apple from the right side of the sink.
Carry the apple and turn around, and a few steps right, to the stove.
Place the apple in the microwave above and shut the door. Open the microwave and take out the apple and shut the door.
Hold the apple and move a few steps to the left and locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside, shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat and then chill an apple.

high_descs: Go straight, then turn right towards the sink. Stop in front of the sink.
Pick up the green apple from the sink.
Turn around, go in front of the stop top.
Put the apple in the microwave, turn on the microwave, remove the apple from the microwave.
Turn left, go in front of the refrigerator.
Put the apple in the refrigerator in front of and to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Cross the room and take a right and then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the green apple from the sink.
Turn around and face the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave and heat it and then take it out and close the door.
Go left and face the fridge on the right.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.
